| valign="middle" style="padding:0 1em; color:#999999; text-align:center" | ''Once you get your hands on the Rice, you can't get rid of it.<br>Even Aurielle, brandishing the grandest military these yellowed halls have seen, doesn't want you to know that this is their true standard issue firearm.<br>Not any of the HK33s, M16s, BRC-TZs, not even the venerable Kalashnikov, but this ol' reliable beauty that's always on your side when logistics can fall apart in mere minutes.'' 
| valign="bottom" style="color:#444444; font-size:3.6em ;font-family:Trajan Pro; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 0;" | „
